  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[DEVIL GIRL NEEDS YOUR MASSAGE]</h2>Devil Girl, Heroine of this Manga book, has no Mana. She needs to recharge her Mana. <br>Devils of this book can recharge Mana by getting human’s touch. <br>You are the only one who can recharge Mana of this Devil Girl.<br>Give her your Massage and make her Mana full<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[HOW TO PLAY]</h2>You can use 5-types of massage skills(Hand Massage, Spanking Massage, Viberator Massage, Electric Massage, Oil Massaage).<br>You have to use the massage skill that Devil Girl wants to get.<br>If Devil Girl's Mana is fully recharged, you can go the next page!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[PLAY GUIDE]</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956550/extras/119505db6e8ffdebfe9bb4fcedaf7f90.avif?t=1548828819\" width=300 height=300 /></span><br>1. Watch carefully what massage Devil Girl wants. She wants Electric Massage!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956550/extras/a1e83dee56ecec20da0ae69aa84fb0a8.avif?t=1548828819\" width=300 height=300 /></span><br>2. Give her what she wants. Press 'F' to give her Electric Massage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/956550/extras/5e982440101babbd0121d5dfa5159212.avif?t=1548828819\" width=300 height=300 /></span><br>3. She loves it! Also, you can see her Mana increase(purple-color background)",
